stories.text:
A lot of people asked when Five/Three/One would be on Android when it made the front page a couple of weeks ago. That day has arrived!

I've already made $70 from IAP in the two initial weeks, which is more than I expected. My goal for now is to make a grand total of a grand, like I did with the iOS app (which is now making >$500/mo [0]).

Anyways, this is not the end of the journey. I'm starting work on another tiny project for now, but will work on an Apple Watch companion for Five/Three/One after that.

Hope you enjoy and get stronger!

[0] https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=31508009
